[h4 id=Mission11:SAVINGPRIVATERIND 
	" Mission 11: SAVING PRIVATE RIND
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"I promote a Sniper to Commando, so I finally have access to a bunch of powerful weapons for any situation and I don't have to deal with straight rifle shots to hit enemies.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Your unit placements on this map are based on your ranks - the most promoted one is in the middle of the map, hidden in the shelter.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"There are 4 hidden Snipers around the middle of the map and one Bombardier who is far from everyone. You can notice a delayed attack on my first turn. This is the 2nd place you can get a softlock for attacking too fast (you can see how it looks in Bloopers).
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"For the next turns I want to kill the enemy units as soon as they're revealed from camouflage, ideally by letting them die on minefields. The order for the last 2 kills was changed because it's faster to kill closer units.
	$LF
