	$LF
	"This is another mission where you can softlock on the first turn so I delay my first aistrike, which kills 2 units.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"The AI's Commando is placed in a very uncomfortable position: most of my shots made him fall somewhere on the low ground, which makes a OHKO impossible for Pyrotechnics. I failed to find a OHKO shot in my old run, but I figured out that making the first airburst's shell explode above the Commando solves this problem.
	[br 
